    "This allows more flexibility in shaping the broadband unvoice filter.",
    "However, we constrain b t û to be larger than 2,000 Hz to capture the wide spectral range of obstruent phonemes.",
    "Instead of using only the broadband filter, we also retain the N formant filters in the voice pathway F t i for the noise pathway.",
    "This is based on the observation that humans perceive consonants such as /p/ and /d/ not only by their initial bursts but also by their subsequent formant transitions until the next vowel 52.",
